responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "8D1D1F094848B53E9AF87480B21ECB9C", "Their bovine stench permeates the air. It is quite unbearable. They have taken hold of the ruins of Thanalas, what was the lair of the Highwayman and his Forsaken Blades. On any other day this would be welcome news, but rumor is that the minos seek the ancient Horn of Doom.")
